{
  "stem": "22889.5",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They didn't want to live any longer.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we used to clean up the canals, always, always to find people laying dead down there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to kill themself.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was a lot of stuff was growing, algae, stuff like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Smelled terrible from the water because it wasn't running water.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The water just lays in the, in the trenches like.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From then on, I was sent to, to Buna, Monowitz.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We marched to the town from Birkenau to Buna, marched about three or five miles.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We marched like that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There were few-- bunch of us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We came to Buna.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There's no place for us again, so they put up tents.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "There were two big tents.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So we slept in the tents for a while till I find final quarters in the barracks, which I slept on the barrack number 28.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I was assigned to build, to baukommando, the building kommando, because they knew what I was doing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They had my record.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] So I was again in a building kommando.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And every-- there were-- we were divided on the groups, for instance, when you go to work.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My kommando number was 48.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "There were 80 of us, maybe, something like that.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And every group had his leader which we called kapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "My kapo was a Jewish fellow.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He was a German fellow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He was a great guy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "His name was [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a great fellow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He never harm us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sometime the kapo cooperated with the SS troopers, you know?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They used to beat the hell out of you, too, the kapos.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Every morning we used to get up around 5 o'clock in the morning from our barracks.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
